text: Hühnerberg may refer to: *Hühnerberg (Wetterau), a low hill of Hesse, Germany *Hühnerberg (Swabia), a mountain of Bavaria, Germany *Hühnerberg (Lommersdorf), a mountain in the Ahr Hills, in the Eifel region, Germany *Hühnerberg (Kirchsahr), a mountain in the Ahr Hills, in the Eifel region, Germany *Hühnerberg (Taunus), a mountain in the Rheingau-Taunus-Kreis, Taunus region, Hesse, Germany ==See also== *Hünerberg, a mountain in the Hochtaunuskreis, Taunus region, Hesse, Germany
title: Hühnerberg
